Library:
	Purpose:		Low risk PWS for alcohol use.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       ;;
	Explanation:	Most adolescents will use alcohol or other drugs before age 21.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     ;;
